| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1583 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7f5d6b4d-84d7-5ee5-9784-f99e9f660fc8"
